featured_reviews.review_id: Kula Kitchen is an Afro Vegan food business and the people who work so hard behind the scenes to prepare all these super delicious meals are such angels!! Going to pick up your order is always a treat and the highlight of my week. I talk about them a lot on my Instagram but thought I would share a review on here for those not on Instagram! Go check out all the wonderful options and dishes they have! Same week delivery or pick up options, if you order by Wednesday night, you can usually pick up or have it delivered by that Saturday! Exceptional service, quick communication and really great value! Try them out today
